%E8%A1%9D%E7%A4%BA%E5%A8%81%E8%80%85%E8%B7%AF%E9%9A%9C%E8%B5%B7%E6%8E%A8%E6%92%9E-%E5%8F%B8%E6%A9%9F%E6%8D%B1%E6%89%93&d=FZf2Eq7oNugCj0cVmX%2F%2FqTizWcNDgH0nsvPDQhA%2BiAk%3D&h=c7f75715\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fpns%2F%E8%A6%81%E8%81%9E%2Farticle%2F20190722%2Fs00001%2F1563736946823%2F%E5%AE%A2%E8%B2%A8%E8%BB%8A%E5%9C%96%E8%A1%9D%E7%A4%BA%E5%A8%81%E8%80%85%E8%B7%AF%E9%9A%9C%E8%B5%B7%E6%8E%A8%E6%92%9E-%E5%8F%B8%E6%A9%9F%E6%8D%B1%E6%89%93&h=6c1a5ab6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://m.mingpao.com/pns/要聞/article/20190722/s00001/1563736946823/客貨車圖衝示威者路障起推撞-司機捱打</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n【明報專訊】一批示威者昨日佔領中環附近的一段馬路，當中一輛客貨車在干諾道中往上環方向的路段，遭示威者擺下的路障阻礙，客貨車一度企圖衝破路障遭示威者阻止，客貨車司機其後落車，與示威者爭執及口角，其間有示威者希望重新擺設路障時，司機上前推撞示威者，觸發雙方衝突，司機被圍毆，現場義工及急救員其後分隔雙方，客貨車司機被打傷由救護員送院治理。打鬥期間，客貨車被人破壞，擋風玻璃及多塊玻璃破裂。<br />\n<br />\n司機郁手先"},{"pid":"83bfd06c7f91e0804c1495fa5717ebe6584ee7d1","tid":1345490,"uid":286763,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"d48e27bb58d5754d730ee9e65405e7f24935a408","tid":1345490,"uid":43510,"like":0,"dislike":7,"score":-7,"quote":{"pid":"d134c50164aadaf92bc17726af40a664e2e66ca5","tid":1345490,"uid":43510,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T01:38:43.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/vet9F3CbSBY\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2Fvet9F3CbSBY&d=FZf2Eq7oNugCj0cVmX%2F%2FqTizWcNDgH0nsvPDQhA%2BiAk%3D&h=c20bac82\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/vet9F3CbSBY</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/TQCkb7v.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FTQCkb7v.gif&h=17a20adf&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n留意雪糕筒<br />\n<br />\n今次水洗都唔清"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T01:43:40.000Z","msg":"攞車撞人係文宣整出黎既fake news"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T17:13:25.000Z","msg":"而家係港人反抗警暴既內戰呀<br />\nCivil War!<br />\n有晒檄文，有晒預告<br />\n佢自己衝入個戰場，擾亂防線，抵打<br />\n<br />\n元朗係無差别恐襲平民，根本無得比<br />\n<br />\n藍屍收得皮啦"},{"pid":"0cc678b18309d99e37